data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
Shitty Server Blocker was created so you can finally stop joining those shitty modded servers when you're just trying to have some Vanilla-styled fun. _______________________________________________________________________________
What does it do?
Well, it simply creates a Windows Firewall rule that stops your connection to the server's IP address. Yes, you could do this manually... But why would you?
_______________________________________________________________________________
FYI - You don't have to use this for just Left 4 Dead servers. _______________________________________________________________________________
